title: 11/18/20 HOUR 2- Mike Florio, Chris Mannix
itunes:title: 11/18/20 HOUR 2- Mike Florio, Chris Mannix
description:
Mike Florio tries to explain to Dan the playing status of DeAndre Baker with the Kansas City Chiefs. Mike says the whole case fell apart because none of the witnesses were credible. Chris Mannix talks to Dan about tonight's NBA Draft. Dan replayed a prior Mannix prediction that James Wiseman will be the best future big man in this Draft.
